OL,3,CWater cannons deployed on second night
OL,4,Cof unrest in Belfast
OL,6,FRiot police have deployed water
OL,7,Fcannons against demonstrators who lit
OL,8,Ffires and threw projectiles at police
OL,9,Fin Belfast, as authorities prepare for
OL,10,Fa second night of unrest in Northern
OL,11,FIreland.
OL,13,FIt comes after politicians urged calm
OL,14,Ffollowing the Belfast knife attack,
OL,15,Fwith Prime Minister Keir Starmer
OL,16,Fcalling earlier disorder "totally
OL,17,Funjustified".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
