OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781168735
OL,3,CWater cannons deployed on second night
OL,4,Cof unrest in Belfast
OL,6,FFootage showed dozens of men dressed
OL,7,Fall in black and wearing face
OL,8,Fcoverings gathering on Antrim Road in
OL,9,FNewtownabbey, north west of Belfast,
OL,10,Fwhere they could be seen tearing
OL,11,Fbricks from properties and smashing
OL,12,Fpaving stones with sledgehammers to
OL,13,Fcreate projectiles to throw at riot
OL,14,Fpolice.
OL,16,FThey could also be seen taking wheelie
OL,17,Fbins from outside homes and lighting
OL,18,Ffires in them.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
