OL,3,CWater cannons deployed on second night
OL,4,Cof unrest in Belfast
OL,6,FTwo water cannons, located near the
OL,7,FSandyknowes roundabout in
OL,8,FNewtownabbey, were fired by police
OL,9,Ftowards demonstrators who had lit
OL,10,Ffires in the street.
OL,12,FTrafficwatch NI said Sandyknowes
OL,13,Froundabout is "currently closed in all
OL,14,Fapproaches due to an ongoing incident".
OL,16,FNearby, a large Department for
OL,17,FInfrastructure vehicle was in flames
OL,18,Fnext to a line of deployed riot police.
OL,26,@uD@OOUvD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
