OL,3,CWater cannons deployed on second night
OL,4,Cof unrest in Belfast
OL,6,FThe Police Service of Northern Ireland
OL,7,F(PSNI) said officers have "deployed
OL,8,Fthe water cannon" to maintain public
OL,9,Forder after missiles were thrown at
OL,10,Fpolice.
OL,12,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FIn a post on social media, the PSNI
OL,18,Fsaid: "Motorists advised to avoid the
OL,19,FSandyknowes Roundabout area of
OL,20,FNewtownabbey due to ongoing disorder
OL,21,Fthis evening.
OL,26,@oD@[OUpD@QO]zD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
