OL,3,CWater cannons deployed on second night
OL,4,Cof unrest in Belfast
OL,6,F"Crowds have gathered & missiles are
OL,7,Fbeing thrown at officers who have now
OL,8,Fdeployed the water cannon in an
OL,9,Fattempt to maintain public order."
OL,11,FOfficers are expecting further
OL,12,Fdisorder in Belfast, alongside a
OL,13,Fplanned peaceful protest that is
OL,14,Fexpected to be attended by over 100
OL,15,Fpeople near Stormont.
OL,17,FIn Derry, police reported items having
OL,18,Fbeen set alight on the Ardmore Road.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
