OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781168735
OL,3,CWater cannons deployed on second night
OL,4,Cof unrest in Belfast
OL,6,FThe violence saw groups of masked
OL,7,Fmales set fire to bins, buses, and
OL,8,Falso homes, with some reporting that
OL,9,Fresidents were targeted based on their
OL,10,Fskin colour.
OL,12,FTwenty-seven people were made homeless
OL,13,Fon Tuesday night, according to the
OL,14,Fgovernment, and police said a two-
OL,15,Fmonth-old baby was among those rescued
OL,16,Fduring the violence.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
