OL,3,CWater cannons deployed on second night
OL,4,Cof unrest in Belfast
OL,6,FThe suspect, Hadi Alodid, appeared
OL,7,Fbefore Belfast Magistrates' Court on
OL,8,FWednesday morning and will be remanded
OL,9,Fin custody until his next court
OL,10,Fappearance in four weeks.
OL,12,FAlodid is a Sudanese national who
OL,13,Fclaimed asylum upon arrival in
OL,14,FSeptember 2023 and was granted leave
OL,15,Fto remain in the UK until 2028.
OL,17,FHe was charged with attempted murder
OL,18,Fwith threats to kill an NHS
OL,19,Fradiographer and with possession of a
OL,20,Fknife.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
