OL,3,CWater cannons deployed on second night
OL,4,Cof unrest in Belfast
OL,6,FThe victim, identified as Stephen
OL,7,FOgilvy, lost his left eye and suffered
OL,8,Fdeep cuts to his head, face and back.
OL,9,FHe remains in hospital.
OL,11,FIn a statement issued through DUP
OL,12,FAssembly member Phillip Brett, the
OL,13,Ffamily of the victim said they are
OL,14,F"devastated by the horrific attack".
OL,16,FThey thanked those who stepped in
OL,17,Fwhile the attack was happening,
OL,18,Fcrediting their actions as life-saving.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
